\c 11
\s Ukuduha kukaSolomoni
\p
\v 1 Inkosi uSolomoni\x + Neh. 13.26.\x* yayithanda-ke abafazi abanengi bezizweni\x + Dute. 17.17.\x*, kanye lendodakazi kaFaro, amaMowabikazi, amaAmonikazi, amaEdomikazi, amaSidonikazi, amaHethikazi\x + 10.29.\x*,
\v 2 ababevela ezizweni iN\nd kosi\nd* eyayithe ngazo kubantwana bakoIsrayeli: Kaliyikungena kibo, labo kabayikungena kini; isibili bazaphendula inhliziyo yenu ilandele onkulunkulu babo. Bona uSolomoni wabanamathela ngothando\x + Eks. 34.16.\x*.
\v 3 Wayelabafazi abangamakhulu ayisikhombisa, amakhosazana, labafazi abancane abangamakhulu amathathu; abafazi bakhe basebephambula inhliziyo yakhe.
\v 4 Ngoba kwathi esikhathini sokuluphala kukaSolomoni, abafazi bakhe baphambulela inhliziyo yakhe ekulandeleni abanye onkulunkulu\x + Josh. 23.12,13.\x*, lenhliziyo yakhe yayingaphelelanga kuJehova uNkulunkulu wakhe\x + 8.61.\x*, njengenhliziyo kaDavida uyise\x + 9.4.\x*.
\v 5 Ngoba uSolomoni wahamba emva kukaAshitarothi unkulunkulu wamaSidoni lemva kukaMilkomu isinengiso samaAmoni\x + 11.33. 2 Kho. 23.13. Hlu. 2.13. 1 Sam. 7.3. 12.10. 31.10.\x*.
\v 6 USolomoni wasesenza okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd*, kayilandelanga ngokupheleleyo iN\nd kosi\nd* njengoDavida uyise.
\v 7 Ngalesosikhathi uSolomoni wakhela uKemoshi\x + 11.33. Nani 21.29.\x* isinengiso sakoMowabi indawo ephakemeyo\x + Nani 33.52.\x* entabeni ephambi kweJerusalema\x + 2 Kho. 23.13.\x*, loMoleki isinengiso sabantwana bakoAmoni\x + 11.5,33. Levi 18.21. 20.2,3,4. 2 Kho. 23.10. Amos 5.26. Zef. 1.5. Seb. 7.43.\x*.
\v 8 Langokunjalo wabenzela bonke abafazi bakhe bezizweni abatshisa impepha bahlabela onkulunkulu babo.
\p
\v 9 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasimthukuthelela uSolomoni, ngoba inhliziyo yakhe yayiphambukile eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli\x + 11.2,3,4.\x*, eyayibonakele kuye kabili\x + 3.5. 9.2.\x*,
\v 10 yamlaya mayelana lalinto, ukuthi angalandeli abanye onkulunkulu; kodwa kagcinanga lokho iN\nd kosi\nd* eyamlaya khona\x + 6.12. 9.6.\x*.
\v 11 Ngakho iN\nd kosi\nd* yathi kuSolomoni: Ngenxa yokuthi lokhu kwenziwe nguwe, ungagcinanga isivumelwano sami lezimiso zami, engakulaya khona, ngizawudabula lokuwudabula umbuso kuwe, ngiwunike inceku yakho\x + 11.31. 12.15,16.\x*.
\v 12 Kanti kangiyikukwenza ensukwini zakho ngenxa kaDavida uyihlo; ngizawudabula usuke esandleni sendodana yakho.
\v 13 Loba kunjalo kangiyikudabula wonke umbuso\x + 2 Sam. 7.15. Hlab. 89.33.\x*; ngizanika indodana yakho isizwe esisodwa ngenxa kaDavida inceku yami langenxa yeJerusalema\x + 11.32,36. 12.20.\x* engiyikhethileyo\x + Dute. 12.5.\x*.
\s Izitha zikaSolomoni
\p
\v 14 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasimvusela uSolomoni isitha, uHadadi umEdoma; wayengowenzalo yenkosi eEdoma.
\v 15 Ngoba kwathi uDavida eseEdoma, uJowabi induna yebutho wayenyukele ukungcwaba ababuleweyo, watshaya wonke owesilisa eEdoma.
\v 16 Ngoba uJowabi wahlala lapho inyanga eziyisithupha, loIsrayeli wonke, waze waquma wonke owesilisa eEdoma.
\v 17 Kodwa uHadadi wabaleka, yena lamaEdoma athile avela encekwini zikayise kanye laye, ukungena eGibhithe; njalo uHadadi wayengumfanyana\x + 2 Sam. 8.14. 1 Lan. 18.12,13.\x*.
\v 18 Basebesuka eMidiyani\x + Hlu. 6.1.\x*, bafika eParani\x + Nani 10.12. Dute. 33.2.\x*, bathatha amadoda labo eParani, bafika eGibhithe, kuFaro inkosi yeGibhithe, owamnika indlu, wammisela ukudla, wamnika umhlabathi.
\v 19 UHadadi wasethola umusa omkhulu emehlweni kaFaro, waze wamendisela udadewabo womkakhe, udadewabo kaTapenesi indlovukazi\x + 15.13. 2 Kho. 10.13. 2 Lan. 15.16. Jer. 13.18. 29. 2.\x*.
\v 20 Udadewabo kaTapenesi wasemzalela uGenubathi indodana yakhe, uTapenesi amlumulela phakathi kwendlu kaFaro; njalo uGenubathi wayesendlini kaFaro phakathi kwabantwana bakaFaro.
\v 21 Kwathi uHadadi esezwile eseGibhithe ukuthi uDavida ulele laboyise lokuthi uJowabi induna yebutho usefile, uHadadi wathi kuFaro: Ngivumela ngisuke ukuthi ngiye elizweni lakithi\x + 2.10,34.\x*.
\v 22 UFaro wasesithi kuye: Kodwa usweleni ulami ukuthi, khangela, udinge ukuya elizweni lakini? Wasesithi: Akulalutho\f + \fk akulalutho: \fl Heb. \fq hatshi.\f*, loba kunjalo ngivumela lokungivumela ngihambe.
\p
\v 23 UNkulunkulu wasemvusela isitha, uRezoni indodana kaEliyada owayebalekile enkosini yakhe uHadadezeri inkosi yeZoba\x + 2 Sam. 10.16.\x*.
\v 24 Wasezibuthela amadoda, waba ngumkhokheli weviyo, lapho uDavida ebabulala\x + 2 Sam. 8.3. 10.8,18.\x*; basebesiya eDamaseko\x + 15.18. 19.15. 20.34. Gen. 14.15. 15.2. 2 Sam. 8.6. 2 Kho. 5.12. 8.7. 14.28. 16.9,10. 1 Lan. 18.5,6. 2 Lan. 24.23. 28.5,23. Isa. 7.8.\x*, bahlala kuyo, babusa eDamaseko.
\v 25 Wasesiba yisitha kuIsrayeli insuku zonke zikaSolomoni, phezu kobubi uHadadi \add abenzayo\add*; njalo wanengwa nguIsrayeli, wabusa phezu kukaSiriya.
\p
\v 26 LoJerobhowamu, indodana kaNebati\x + 12.2. 2 Lan. 13.6.\x*, umEfrayimi\x + Gen. 35.19. 1 Sam. 1.1. 17.12. Hlab. 132.6.\x* weZereda\x + Josh. 3.16. 2 Lan. 4.17.\x*, inceku kaSolomoni, obizo likanina lalinguZeruwa, owesifazana ongumfelokazi, laye waphakamisa isandla emelene lenkosi\x + 2 Sam. 20.21.\x*.
\v 27 Yilolu-ke udaba lokuthi aphakamise isandla emelene lenkosi\x + 2 Sam. 20.21.\x*. USolomoni wakha iMilo\x + 9.24. 2 Sam. 5.9.\x*, wavala isikhala somuzi kaDavida uyise.
\v 28 UJerobhowamu wayeliqhawe elilamandla. Kwathi uSolomoni ebona lelijaha ukuthi likhuthele emsebenzini, walibeka phezu kwawo wonke umthwalo wendlu kaJosefa.
\v 29 Kwasekusithi ngalesosikhathi lapho uJerobhowamu ephuma eJerusalema, uAhiya\x + 12.15. 14.2. 15.29. 2 Lan. 9.29.\x* umShilo\x + Josh. 18.1.\x* umprofethi wamfica endleleni. Njalo wayezigqokise isigqoko esitsha; bobabili babebodwa egangeni.
\v 30 UAhiya wasesibamba isigqoko esitsha esasikuye, wasidabula iziqa ezilitshumi lambili\x + 2 Kho. 2.12. 1 Sam. 15.27.\x*,
\v 31 wathi kuJerobhowamu: Zithathele iziqa ezilitshumi, ngoba itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli: Khangela, ngizadabula umbuso usuke esandleni sikaSolomoni, ngikunike izizwe ezilitshumi\x + 11.11,13.\x*.
\v 32 Kodwa yena uzakuba lesizwe esisodwa ngenxa yenceku yami uDavida langenxa yeJerusalema, umuzi engiwukhethileyo ezizweni zonke zakoIsrayeli.
\v 33 Ngenxa yokuthi bangitshiyile, bakhonza uAshitarothi unkulunkulu wamaSidoni\x + 11.5.\x*, uKemoshi unkulunkulu wamaMowabi\x + 11.7.\x*, loMilkomu unkulunkulu wabantwana bakoAmoni\x + 11.5.\x*, kabahambanga ngendlela zami, ukwenza okulungileyo emehlweni ami, lo\add kulondoloza\add* izimiso zami lezahlulelo zami, njengoDavida uyise.
\v 34 Loba kunjalo kangiyikuwususa umbuso wonke esandleni sakhe; kodwa ngizamenza abe ngumbusi zonke izinsuku zempilo yakhe ngenxa kaDavida inceku yami, engamkhethayo, owagcina imilayo yami lezimiso zami\x + 11.12.\x*.
\v 35 Kodwa ngizawususa umbuso esandleni sendodana yakhe, ngiwunike wena, izizwe ezilitshumi\x + 12.15,16,17.\x*.
\v 36 Lendodana yakhe ngizayinika isizwe sibe sinye ukuze uDavida inceku yami abe lesibane zonke izinsuku phambi kwami eJerusalema\x + 11.13,32. 12.21,23.\x*, umuzi engizikhethele wona ukuze ngibeke ibizo lami khona\x + 11.32. 14.21. Dute. 12.5.\x*.
\v 37 Wena-ke ngizakuthatha, uzabusa phezu kwakho konke umphefumulo wakho okuloyisayo, ube yinkosi phezu kukaIsrayeli.
\v 38 Kuzakuthi-ke, uba ulalela konke engikulaya khona, uhambe ngezindlela zami, wenze okulungileyo emehlweni ami, ukugcina izimiso zami lemilayo yami, njengokwenza kukaDavida inceku yami, ngizakuba lawe\x + Josh. 1.5.\x*, ngikwakhele indlu eqinileyo, njengengayakhela uDavida, ngizakunika uIsrayeli\x + 1 Sam. 2.35.\x*,
\v 39 njalo ngihluphe inzalo kaDavida ngenxa yalokhu, kodwa kungabi kokuphela.
\v 40 Ngakho uSolomoni wadinga ukumbulala uJerobhowamu, kodwa uJerobhowamu wasuka wabalekela eGibhithe, kuShishaki inkosi yeGibhithe, wayeseGibhithe waze wafa uSolomoni\x + 14.25. 2 Lan. 12.2,5,7,9.\x*.
\s Ukufa kukaSolomoni
\p
\v 41 Ezinye-ke zezindaba zikaSolomoni, lakho konke akwenzayo, lenhlakanipho yakhe, kakubhalwanga yini egwalweni lwendaba zikaSolomoni\x + 2 Lan. 9.29-31.\x*?
\v 42 Isikhathi-ke uSolomoni abusa ngaso eJerusalema phezu kukaIsrayeli wonke saba yiminyaka engamatshumi amane.
\v 43 USolomoni waselala laboyise\x + 2.10. 14.20.\x*, wangcwatshelwa emzini kaDavida uyise\x + 2.10. 14.20.\x*. URehobhowamu indodana yakhe wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe\x + Mat. 1.7.\x*.